        <div class="info-line"><span class="info-label">📍 University</span> Virtual University of Pakistan</div>
        <div class="info-line"><span class="info-label">📧 Email</span> haseebarif112234@gmail.com</div>
        <div class="info-line"><span class="info-label">🐙 GitHub</span> <a href="https://github.com/haseeb-linux" target="_blank">github.com/haseeb-linux</a></div>
