      <em>“Linux terminal open + C++ book + networking notes — building my future step by step.”</em>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Muhammad Haseeb — IT Student | Virtual University of Pakistan</p>
      <p>📧 <a href="mailto:haseebarif112234@gmail.com">haseebarif112234@gmail.com</a> | 🐙 <a href="https://github.com/haseeb-linux" target="_blank">haseeb-linux</a></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">✨ Designed with ❤️ | Pure HTML/CSS | GitHub Pages ✨</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
